c: 10
v: 18
t: "And they worship, apart from Allah, what neither harms them nor profits them; and they say, \"These are our intercessors in the Providence of Allah.\" Say, \"Do you really inform Allah of what He does not know (either) in the heavens or in the earth?\" All Extolment be to Him! And Supremely Exalted be He above whatever they associate"